Develop an APP that simulates Walkie Talkie but with the features customized by mobile internet concept.
Some projecting features:
1. Point to point talking and texting.
2. Broadcast (voice & message)
3. No central server sitting in between. Only for storing contact info.
4. Free to one P2P connection and one broadcast band.
5. Could be a radio.
6. Charge for specific band and public band number.

